name: LOBISOMEM - Xylography #05
description:
LOBISOMEM (The werewolf) is a popular legend all over the world. In northeastern Brazil, it is common to hear from the elderly stories of people who have seen or met a werewolf. As a child, I heard many of these stories. 
Usually the werewolf manifests itself on nights when the moon is full. And if the night is a "Blood Moon", lock your doors.

Attention: Zoom in for a better appreciation.
